🏁 Driver Announcement 🏁 

@remstar_racing and @fastmdracing are thrilled to introduce Jagger Jones as the featured driver for the upcoming IMSA VP Racing SportsCar Challenge! 🚗💨

Among the standout candidates was the remarkable Jagger Jones, whose racing pedigree is truly outstanding. 

As the grandson of the legendary racer and 1963 Indy 500 winner, Parnelli Jones, Jagger’s passion for racing runs in his veins. 🏆 Currently, he is making waves in the INDY NXT series by Firestone, showcasing his immense potential on the track. 🔥

Mike Hull, Managing Director at Chip Ganassi Racing, fully supports this decision: ‘It’s exciting that Remi Lantinga has chosen Jagger Jones based upon his talent to represent Remstar in the VP Challenge at Petit. Jagger’s proven versatility to win from a young age that started in Karting and then forward into open-and closed wheel racing provides him an opportunity to be showcased to an IMSA audience. The global sports car racing growth is being strengthened by the talented youth movement. Jagger fits what the next teammate generation provides: natural talent tempered equally by an ethic to unselfishly share.’ 🏎️

Stay tuned for a thrilling race at Michelin Raceway Road Atlanta circuit on October 11th-13th. 💥
